name: jam cat
description: Jam Cat ($JAM) is a Solana-based meme token rooted in a viral animation of a rhythmically bobbing cat. The original meme gained over one million organic views across platforms such as TikTok, Tenor, and Instagram. Building on this meme momentum, the project developed an AI agent that creates cat-themed, finance-infused poetry and content, primarily posted on X (formerly Twitter). $JAM serves as the native token supporting the Jam Cat brand and community ecosystem.
